---

<section id="about" class="fade-up">
  <div class="section-tag">About</div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        I'm <strong>Nico Hermida</strong>, a fullstack developer from Argentina. I started programming on my own 6 years ago, long before entering university — which gave me a practical edge that my degree later formalized.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently in my 4th year of a <strong>Computer Science degree</strong>, with <strong>1 year of professional experience</strong> at a startup, I bring a profile that combines technical depth with the ability to build products from scratch.
      </p>
      <p>
        I specialize in the <span class="about-highlight">Node / NestJS + Next.js stack</span>, and I'm currently deepening my knowledge in Python backend with FastAPI and mobile development with React Native.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-stats">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">5+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">years developing web projects</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">1</div>
        <div class="stat-label">year of professional experience</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">4to</div>
        <div class="stat-label">year, Computer Science degree</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 60px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Texto */
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .about-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--cyan));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Stats */
  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(37, 99, 240, 0.3);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--cyan));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    #about {
      padding: 80px 24px;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .about-text p {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>